parameters:
Celis, the Gale: You've arrived. This is the place where the
factory used to be.

Celis, the Gale: Dragon tears have an unknown manufacturing
method, so I want you to investigate the manufacturing
method here.

Clea: Understood, I will try to find hints about the
manufacturing method.

Celis of the Swift Wind: I'm fine. It was the right call to
be cautious at the entrance. The enemy noticed our
movements.

Clea: This is the recipe I found and a memo about where it's
distributed.

Celis of the Swift Wind: The ingredients are discarded
crystals...!

Celis of the Swift Wind: Let's go to the warehouse in the
Marako Village where it's distributed. If we leave it alone,
the empire will be thrown into chaos.
